  <brief_title>Use of Prothrombin Complex Concentrate in Patients Admitted in Emergency Care Units for Severe Bleeding While Receiving Oral Anticoagulants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Administration of PCC in Patients Admitted in Emergency Care Units for Severe Bleeding While Receiving Oral Anticoagulants: Impact of an Expert ECRF on Adherence to Rules of Proper Use and Outcome</official_title>
