  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is assessing the impact of an expert eCRF on the management of severe bleeding in
      the administration of Prothrombin Complex Concentrate in patients treated with oral
      anticoagulants and adherence to recommendations or experts' consensus
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
